snippet.title: «Last Memories» Game trailer.
snippet.description:
«Last memories» is a short point&click adventure. A dark story about a short but tragic journey. Adventure game with a rich storyline and multiple endings.

Game is available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2271060/Last_Memories/
